data.description: Discover the epitome of comfortable living in this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom pool home located in the sought-after Dr. Phillips area. With separate living and dining spaces, a cozy family room, and a delightful dinette nook, this residence seamlessly combines functionality with style.    Appreciate modern design elements in the pool area, perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Recent updates include a new roof in 2021, pool filter replacement in 2021, a new A/C unit from 2015, a new garage opener, a new electrical panel, electrical wiring for a potential pool heater, a new garage system, and a tankless water heater.    This home features high vaulted ceilings, creating a sense of space and sophistication. The kitchen is adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, enhancing the heart of the home.    Enjoy the convenience of the location, close to Millenia Mall, I-4, Universal Studios, Restaurant Row, and major highways. With a top-rated school system, this house is a must-see. Schedule your tour today – it will not last long. Come and make this updated residence your new home!
